Surgical Aortic Valve Replacement in the Elderly: It Is Worth It!

Nader J(1), Zainulabdin O(2), Marzouk M(2), Guay S(2), Vasse S(3), Mohammadi 
S(2), Dagenais F(2), Caus T(3), Voisine P(2).

