Cost-effectiveness of percutaneous coronary intervention versus medical therapy 
in patients with acute myocardial infarction: real-world and lifetime-horizon 
data from Taiwan.

Liao CT(1)(2)(3), Hsieh TH(4), Shih CY(2), Liu PY(4), Wang JD(5)(6).

Author information:
(1)Division of Cardiology, Department of Internal Medicine, Chi-Mei Medical 
